value: 8741 - Management Services Summary > WHITTLES GROUP HOLDINGS PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover management services. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. WHITTLES GROUP HOLDINGS PTY LTD is headquartered in Dulwich, South Australia. It is headed by managing director Allan Dalmore Amber. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $37.91 million. Its net profit totalled $6.46 million. WHITTLES GROUP HOLDINGS PTY LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
